thread.title: Man arrested after teenage cyclist killed in Essex collision

author: itv.com
title: Man arrested after teenage cyclist killed in Essex collision
text:
A 15-year-old cyclist has been killed after being hit by a car on Clingoe Hill in Essex.
Credit: PA Paramedics and an air ambulance attended the scene, but the teenager was pronounced dead at the scene.
Essex police arrested a 54-year-old man on suspicion of causing death by careless driving.
Police are appealing for any witnesses to the collision.
